        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "These brown leather shoes have surprisingly thick soles, as though a cobbler had recently repaired them. The tan laces always pull to exactly the right tautness for your feet and ankles to feel supported. You can perform the Hustle exploration mode activity for twice as many minutes as normal, equal to your Constitution modifier \u00d7 20 (minimum 20).",
